(16, 1, '2015-02-22 22:51:56', '2015-02-22 22:51:56', 'Rob Antrim’s vast experience in development and tenant representation are examples of how T.M. Crowley & Associates provide clients with a unique perspective and comfort level for their next project.\r\n\r\nHaving worked closely with clients on development in 10 states, including such name brands as Target and PetSmart, Rob is thoroughly qualified and experienced in many facets of development.\r\n\r\nExperience, coupled with attention to detail, are among the traits that are universal to all members of T.M. Crowley & Associates.', 'Rob Antrim', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'rob-antrim__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=16', 4, 'person', '', 0),
