(23, 1, '2015-02-22 23:10:19', '2015-02-22 23:10:19', 'AJ Barbato brings a track record of success for our clients. His expertise in ground up development includes every facet of the process from initial site selection through entitlement approvals, financing and the ultimate turnover of a successful project.  AJ has documented years of experience leading a team of brokers, client counsel, architectural and engineering firms as well as local municipalities, consistently driving projects to an ultimate successful completion.  \r\n\r\nHe has been intricately involved in development of numerous properties in Maine, New York, New Hampshire, Massachusetts, Connecticut, Indiana, Illinois and Wisconsin facilitating the growth of major corporations. \r\n\r\nWith a background in finance, AJ is perfectly positioned to make sure our clients receive the greatest return and the most value on their investment.  ', 'AJ Barbato', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'aj-barbato__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=23', 3, 'person', '', 0),
