(29, 1, '2015-02-22 23:14:42', '2015-02-22 23:14:42', 'Brenda Bryant is the executive administrative assistant for Tom Crowley.\r\n\r\nShe has been an administrative assistant for more than 26 years and has worked with Tom for 14 years. Brenda also provides administrative support for legal counsel, development and marketing.\r\n\r\nPrior to working for Tom Crowley, Brenda worked for 12 years at Simon Property Group, Indianapolis, Ind.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, experience is one of our greatest assets.', 'Brenda Bryant', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'brenda-bryant__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=29', 4, 'person', '', 0),
