(36, 1, '2015-02-22 23:18:15', '2015-02-22 23:18:15', 'As COO, Chris brings over 20 years of experience in Financial Reporting, Project Budgeting, Operational Forecasts, Property Management, Financial Analysis and Cash Management, as well as Benefits Administration, 401k Compliance and Human Resources.\r\n\r\nChris works with key team members in the evaluation of potential developments. She assists in securing funding for ground-up development projects. In addition, Chris creates operational budgets and forecasts for multiple properties.\r\n\r\nShe also executes the day-to-day business transactions of the company as well as the administration of employee benefits, insurance, 401k plan and internal controls.\r\n\r\nChris is a licensed real estate broker.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, we believe leadership is one of the keys to your success', 'Chris Daumeyer', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'chris-daumeyer__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=36', 1, 'person', '', 0),
