(54, 1, '2015-02-22 23:18:52', '2015-02-22 23:18:52', 'Lou Eyster is part of our construction management team and is focused on facilitating all aspects of the project management and development process for our clients. This includes permitting, budget and schedule control, value engineering and construction.\r\n\r\nLou has more than seven years of experience working on large scale expansion and renovation projects serving both the public and private sector.\r\n\r\nHe is a LEED Accredited Professional and a licensed real estate broker.', 'Lou Eyster', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'lou-eyster__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=54', 1, 'person', '', 0),
