(56, 1, '2015-02-22 23:19:09', '2015-02-22 23:19:09', 'As VP of Construction, Craig is responsible for managing the design, permitting and construction development process of both large scale and single tenant developments. Craig works closely with clients, architects and engineers, local and state regulatory agencies and contractors to complete construction projects from their inception all the way through completion of construction and delivery to the client. Craig oversees multiple projects at any given time and has proven capable of delivering multiple fast-pace projects on time by juggling responsibilities, managing non-flexible schedules, providing quick problem solution and effectively managing the client’s needs while exceeding their expectations.\r\n\r\nCraig is a Licensed Professional Engineer.', 'Craig Forgey', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'craig-forgey__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=56', 2, 'person', '', 0),
