(64, 1, '2015-02-22 23:21:54', '2015-02-22 23:21:54', 'Cody Herbster’s primary focus is the Third Party Development program for T.M. Crowley & Associates.\r\n\r\nHis experience in Sales and Marketing for an industrial manufacturer gave him a base on which to build his skills and offer advice and counsel to our clients as they navigate the development process.\r\n\r\nHis history of success adds to the value that clients of T.M. Crowley & Associates expect.', 'Cody Herbster', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'cody-herbster__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=64', 3, 'person', '', 0),
