(70, 1, '2015-02-22 23:23:41', '2015-02-22 23:23:41', 'Megan Painter is the Accounts Payable Manager for T.M. Crowley & Associates.\r\n\r\nHer duties include submitting and tracking all pre-construction draws and land deposit payments for approval. When draws are funded, she processes payments to the vendors and land owners in a timely manner.\r\nHer scope of responsibilities stretches from the New England states to the Midwest. She is accountable for T.M. Crowley & Associates’ monthly invoices, rental payments and ACH deposits. She participates in monthly conference calls with vendors to review A/R reports.\r\n\r\nMegan also supports our Marketing Department. Megan is a liaison between the client and a project team. The team consists of attorneys, signage vendors, brokers, architects and engineers.\r\n\r\nMegan’s primary focus in her work with the Marketing Department is the on-time delivery of the tour books. The tour books include maps, aerials, site photos, competition profiles and demographic packages associated with our projects.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, our team’s diverse skills work to your advantage.', 'Megan Painter', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'megan-painter__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=70', 6, 'person', '', 0),
