(72, 1, '2015-02-22 23:24:01', '2015-02-22 23:24:01', 'As Regional Real Estate Deal Manager at T.M. Crowley & Associates, Shannon’s responsibilities include managing numerous projects for national clients in the Midwest and New England areas.\r\n\r\nShannon acts as a liaison between our clients and development teams consisting of attorneys, civil engineers, environmental consultants, architects and general contractors. Shannon ensures the projects remain on schedule and deliverables are met on time.\r\n\r\nShannon’s responsibilities also include overseeing the coordination of the purchase and sale agreements or lease signings and tracking operative dates from their execution through closing/possession, at which time she coordinates the assimilation of the closing/possession documents for the client’s outside counsel.\r\nShannon is also responsible for initiating the due diligence process with the environmental consultants and coordinating the entitlement process with civil engineers, architects and attorneys to ensure compliance with the client’s requirements.\r\nShe works closely with the engineers, architects and attorneys through the permitting process to ensure the project remains on schedule. Project tracking reports are issued monthly to ensure adherence to timelines and to provide project updates to the team.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, all of us take a 360-degree view of our responsibilities. Our combined vision creates a picture-perfect result for our clients.', 'Shannon Parker', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'shannon-parker__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=72', 7, 'person', '', 0),
