(74, 1, '2015-02-22 23:24:22', '2015-02-22 23:24:22', 'Sandra brings over 20 years of experience in administrative executive support as well as customer service and market research reporting. She is a graduate of Indiana University and has enjoyed a career in merchandising and management as well as executive administration. Her attention to detail and ability to serve many different support functions within the company make her a highly efficient and valued employee of T.M. Crowley & Associates.', 'Sandra Ritter', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'sandra-ritter__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=74', 18, 'person', '', 0),
