(78, 1, '2015-02-22 23:25:03', '2015-02-22 23:25:03', 'As VP Controller with T.M. Crowley & Associates, Pamela is responsible for overseeing the accounting operations of several real estate development subsidiaries. She also provides project accounting management for several national clients.\r\n\r\nPamela works closely with client financial managers, construction and real estate personnel and vendors to foster successful business relationships. Pamela is involved with each project from the initial budgeting to the final construction closeout process.\r\n\r\nPamela has 12 years experience in project accounting management, consisting primarily of new ground up stores, renovations and expansions. Her responsibilities have involved over 500 stores throughout the country.\r\nShe coordinates with construction personnel, civil engineers, environmental consultants and architects to provide an accurate budget estimate per project to submit for approval. All accounting of project presentation, entitlement procurement and construction costs are managed on a project-by-project basis and processed through T.M. Crowley & Associates.\r\n\r\nAttention to detail is a trademark of T.M. Crowley & Associates.', 'Pamela Whitaker', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'pamela-whitaker__trashed', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '2016-05-02 04:28:18', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=78', 9, 'person', '', 0),
