(120, 1, '2016-02-01 02:39:05', '2016-02-01 02:39:05', 'As Regional Real Estate Deal Manager at T.M. Crowley & Associates, Chris brings a background of managing and overseeing a portfolio of over 65 projects in the New England and New York areas. He has over 15 years of experience in commercial real estate.\r\n\r\nChris acts as a liaison between clients and a development team consisting of environmental consultants, civil engineers, architects, general contractors and attorneys. His primary goal is delivering projects on schedule.\r\n\r\nChris is also responsible for coordinating purchase agreement and lease signings, tracking operative dates from execution through closing/possession, initiating environmental due diligence and coordinating the entitlement process with civil engineers, architects and attorneys. His responsibilities also include ensuring compliance with client requirements, issuing monthly tracking reports on all projects, adherence to timelines/schedules and assimilating closing and possession documentation for outside legal counsel.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, we believe there is no substitute for experience and a proven track record of success.', 'Chris Moretti', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '68-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-01 02:39:05', '2016-02-01 02:39:05', '', 68, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/01/68-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(122, 1, '2016-02-01 02:39:35', '2016-02-01 02:39:35', 'Megan Painter is the Accounts Payable Manager for T.M. Crowley & Associates.\r\n\r\nHer duties include submitting and tracking all pre-construction draws and land deposit payments for approval. When draws are funded, she processes payments to the vendors and land owners in a timely manner.\r\nHer scope of responsibilities stretches from the New England states to the Midwest. She is accountable for T.M. Crowley & Associates’ monthly invoices, rental payments and ACH deposits. She participates in monthly conference calls with vendors to review A/R reports.\r\n\r\nMegan also supports our Marketing Department. Megan is a liaison between the client and a project team. The team consists of attorneys, signage vendors, brokers, architects and engineers.\r\n\r\nMegan’s primary focus in her work with the Marketing Department is the on-time delivery of the tour books. The tour books include maps, aerials, site photos, competition profiles and demographic packages associated with our projects.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, our team’s diverse skills work to your advantage.', 'Megan Painter', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-01 02:39:35', '2016-02-01 02:39:35', '', 70, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/01/70-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(123, 1, '2016-02-01 02:40:00', '2016-02-01 02:40:00', 'As Regional Real Estate Deal Manager at T.M. Crowley & Associates, Shannon’s responsibilities include managing numerous projects for national clients in the Midwest and New England areas.\r\n\r\nShannon acts as a liaison between our clients and development teams consisting of attorneys, civil engineers, environmental consultants, architects and general contractors. Shannon ensures the projects remain on schedule and deliverables are met on time.\r\n\r\nShannon’s responsibilities also include overseeing the coordination of the purchase and sale agreements or lease signings and tracking operative dates from their execution through closing/possession, at which time she coordinates the assimilation of the closing/possession documents for the client’s outside counsel.\r\nShannon is also responsible for initiating the due diligence process with the environmental consultants and coordinating the entitlement process with civil engineers, architects and attorneys to ensure compliance with the client’s requirements.\r\nShe works closely with the engineers, architects and attorneys through the permitting process to ensure the project remains on schedule. Project tracking reports are issued monthly to ensure adherence to timelines and to provide project updates to the team.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, all of us take a 360-degree view of our responsibilities. Our combined vision creates a picture-perfect result for our clients.', 'Shannon Parker', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-01 02:40:00', '2016-02-01 02:40:00', '', 72, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/01/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
