(152, 1, '2016-02-04 05:53:29', '2016-02-04 05:53:29', 'Charlie Haapala is an expert in construction, design and development. He has a wealth of experience in retail fast track, and brand name store roll outs across the country. His history of success includes the establishment of restaurants, department stores, strip centers, mixed use high-rise and loft conversions, town housing, high end residential, hotels, banks, downtown parking garages, office buildings and warehouses.\r\n\r\nCharlie has been integral to the fast track, high volume (+100) simultaneous competitive bid build outs of Lerner’s, Express, The Limited, Victoria’s Secret, Lane Bryant, Lens Crafters, Wilson Suede & Leather, Tucci Benucchi Restaurants, Capitol Commerce Center, Forest Park Mall, J. Alexander Restaurants, Carson Pirie Scott, Barnes & Noble Book Seller and more.\r\n\r\nAs Managing VP of Construction for a Chicagoland developer, Charlie has been responsible for delivering completed projects, including initial site and building design development, specification detailing, city/neighborhood approvals, conceptual budgeting/estimating, contract negotiation and administration, management of in-house construction staff, consultants, architects, engineers, contractors, customer service departments, property management and claim settlements.\r\n\r\nHe successfully delivered more than $80 million in development during this two year phase, including over 375 condos with numerous commercial tenant spaces.\r\n\r\nCharlie has earned a reputation for delivering high quality projects on time and on budget. He is there every step of the way, from initial conceptual budgeting, competitive hard bidding, contract negotiations and award, project management through completion and customer service.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, each member of our team has a history of excellence.', 'Charlie Haapala', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '60-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:53:29', '2016-02-04 05:53:29', '', 60, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/60-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(153, 1, '2016-02-04 05:53:34', '2016-02-04 05:53:34', 'Jason Challand utilizes his wealth of experience by advising clients on their real estate needs. He is a trusted advisor on site selection, land assemblage, contractual negotiations, due diligence, analyzing bids from contractors and builders, project supervision and communication with local governing bodies. Jason is also responsible for facilities acquisition and disposition, tenant and landlord representation, investment and land sales.\r\n\r\nHis expertise is an asset to clients who are considering ownership, investment or leasing. He has created development projects and closed sale and lease transactions that have exceeded $730 million in value.\r\n\r\nJason’s knowledge base includes Tenant/Buyer & Landlord/Investor Advisory Services, Investment Sales and Land Acquisition, as well as Disposition Services. He is a Licensed Indiana Real Estate Broker.\r\n\r\nJason has worked with companies and developers such as Gershman Brown Crowley, Throgmartin Henke Development, Mainstreet Property Group, i3 Worldwide, Level 3 Communications, Midwest Graphics, BremnerDuke Healthcare, Duke Realty, Edgeworth Laskey Properties, First Industrial Realty Trust, Opus North, The Estridge Companies, Fischer Homes, Beazer Homes, NVR/Ryan Homes, Mann Properties, Somerset Financial Services, Krieg DeVault LLP, Doninger Tuohy & Bailey LLP, Nelson & Frankenberger P.C., The Mediation Alternative, Wise Financial, Meyer Najem, The Fazzt Race Team, Five Guys Burgers and Fries, Buffalo Wild Wings, Moe’s Southwest Grill, Taco Bell/Southern Bells, Inc., Hot Box Pizza, Fifth Third Bank, First Merchants Bank and all land planning departments in Indianapolis and the surrounding counties.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, we bring a team of proven professionals to your project.', 'Jason S. Challand', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '82-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:53:34', '2016-02-04 05:53:34', '', 82, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/82-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(154, 1, '2016-02-04 05:53:38', '2016-02-04 05:53:38', 'Brenda Bryant is the executive administrative assistant for Tom Crowley.\r\n\r\nShe has been an administrative assistant for more than 26 years and has worked with Tom for 14 years. Brenda also provides administrative support for legal counsel, development and marketing.\r\n\r\nPrior to working for Tom Crowley, Brenda worked for 12 years at Simon Property Group, Indianapolis, Ind.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, experience is one of our greatest assets.', 'Brenda Bryant', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '29-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:53:38', '2016-02-04 05:53:38', '', 29, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/29-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(155, 1, '2016-02-04 05:53:43', '2016-02-04 05:53:43', 'Sandra brings over 20 years of experience in administrative executive support as well as customer service and market research reporting. She is a graduate of Indiana University and has enjoyed a career in merchandising and management as well as executive administration. Her attention to detail and ability to serve many different support functions within the company make her a highly efficient and valued employee of T.M. Crowley & Associates.', 'Sandra Ritter', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:53:43', '2016-02-04 05:53:43', '', 74, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/74-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(156, 1, '2016-02-04 05:53:57', '2016-02-04 05:53:57', 'Rob Antrim’s vast experience in development and tenant representation are examples of how T.M. Crowley & Associates provide clients with a unique perspective and comfort level for their next project.\r\n\r\nHaving worked closely with clients on development in 10 states, including such name brands as Target and PetSmart, Rob is thoroughly qualified and experienced in many facets of development.\r\n\r\nExperience, coupled with attention to detail, are among the traits that are universal to all members of T.M. Crowley & Associates.', 'Rob Antrim', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:53:57', '2016-02-04 05:53:57', '', 16, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(157, 1, '2016-02-04 05:54:01', '2016-02-04 05:54:01', 'AJ Barbato brings a track record of success for our clients. His expertise in ground up development includes every facet of the process from initial site selection through entitlement approvals, financing and the ultimate turnover of a successful project.  AJ has documented years of experience leading a team of brokers, client counsel, architectural and engineering firms as well as local municipalities, consistently driving projects to an ultimate successful completion.  \r\n\r\nHe has been intricately involved in development of numerous properties in Maine, New York, New Hampshire, Massachusetts, Connecticut, Indiana, Illinois and Wisconsin facilitating the growth of major corporations. \r\n\r\nWith a background in finance, AJ is perfectly positioned to make sure our clients receive the greatest return and the most value on their investment.  ', 'AJ Barbato', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:54:01', '2016-02-04 05:54:01', '', 23, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(158, 1, '2016-02-04 05:54:05', '2016-02-04 05:54:05', 'As COO, Chris brings over 20 years of experience in Financial Reporting, Project Budgeting, Operational Forecasts, Property Management, Financial Analysis and Cash Management, as well as Benefits Administration, 401k Compliance and Human Resources.\r\n\r\nChris works with key team members in the evaluation of potential developments. She assists in securing funding for ground-up development projects. In addition, Chris creates operational budgets and forecasts for multiple properties.\r\n\r\nShe also executes the day-to-day business transactions of the company as well as the administration of employee benefits, insurance, 401k plan and internal controls.\r\n\r\nChris is a licensed real estate broker.\r\n\r\nAt T.M. Crowley & Associates, we believe leadership is one of the keys to your success', 'Chris Daumeyer', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-04 05:54:05', '2016-02-04 05:54:05', '', 36, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/2016/02/04/36-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
