(228, 1, '2016-05-02 04:34:40', '2016-05-02 04:34:40', 'Charles Yoo is a project manager for Proton International’s current and future clients and endeavors. He oversees the life cycle of each project. This includes: feasibility analysis; modeling and financial structuring; oversight of projects under development; and operational advisory services. Charles has 16 years of financial experience with private companies and government involving research, analysis, forecasting and capital markets. Prior to joining Proton International, Mr. Yoo gained over 3 years of proton expertise in center finances and operations at the CDH Proton Center near Chicago, Illinois, the 9th U.S.-Based proton facility. Mr. Yoo holds a Bachelor of Science in Management from Massachusetts Institute of Technology and a Master of Business Administration with Concentrations in Finance and Entrepreneurship from the University of Chicago Booth School of Business.', 'Charles Yoo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'charles-yoo', '', '', '2016-05-02 04:34:40', '2016-05-02 04:34:40', '', 0, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?post_type=person&#038;p=228', 6, 'person', '', 0),
