(271, 1, '2016-05-04 22:49:08', '2016-05-04 22:49:08', 'Successfully operating a flourishing proton therapy center requires expertise, attention to detail and experience in managing through common obstacles. Our team brings more experience to the table than any other, and our operational services ensure your center operates at its greatest capacity.\r\n\r\nOnce your therapy center is built, the key to success lies in high quality standards, a highly competent staff, a comprehensive medical program, treatment protocols and a research program for clinical trial participation. We offer comprehensive services in business operations and organizational setup focused on helping you manage and maintain vital operational aspects of your proton therapy center.\r\n\r\n<strong>Business Operations &amp; Organizational Setup</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We oversee or support the selection of key director-level staff, providing guidance on the hiring qualifications and certifications of all other center staff</li>\r\n 	<li>We set up a tailored metrics and reporting system to enable a more holistic view of the business, allowing for more seamless management</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Site Manager</strong>\r\n\r\nWe provide dedicated site support from your first patient treatment forward. As part of our operational assistance offering, we provide a full-time site manager at your location to manage a number of key activities. This individual is dedicated to serve the needs of your center and serve as a key asset in the organizational learning required for delivering world-class proton therapy. The site manager’s areas of expertise and responsibility include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Oversight and coordination of all proton equipment service contracts</li>\r\n 	<li>Oversight and responsibility for all proton system issues and/or performance improvements</li>\r\n 	<li>Primary point of contact with proton equipment supplier</li>\r\n 	<li>Site-specific project management support, as needed (intake, reimbursement, process improvement, technology, etc.)</li>\r\n 	<li>Site reporting on downtime events and corrective action</li>\r\n 	<li>Oversight and coordination of research protocols conducted in partnership with other centers</li>\r\n 	<li>Coordination and access to other resources in the network to determine and share best practices</li>\r\n 	<li>KPI reporting on all critical system performance metrics as determined by your center</li>\r\n 	<li>Coordination of ongoing physics quality and commissioning services, and oversight of all quality equipment calibration and maintenance</li>\r\n 	<li>Oversight and coordination of any third party contracted services</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Operations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'operations', '', '', '2016-05-09 03:56:59', '2016-05-09 03:56:59', '', 202, 'http://mattritter.design/protonintl/?page_id=271', 0, 'page', '', 0),
